## Intervention Types

**encouragement** (3-day gap)
- Gentle reminder of progress
- Reinforce why practice matters
- Offer low-friction re-entry

**support** (automaticity decline)
- Identify what's blocking practice
- Adjust Kata difficulty if needed
- Offer coaching session

**escalation** (7-day gap — habit decay)
- Alert hKask-Administrator
- Document decay trigger
- Plan restart strategy

